e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/97620/', '', 'Omalizumab, Tezepelumab, Mercaptopurine, Benralizumab, Caffeine, Reslizumab, Montelukast, Dyphylline, Mepolizumab, Pentoxifylline, Bromotheophylline', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Cladribine, More', 1767369485);
